Subject: [PATCH] hw/misc: add VAMS NOP queue transport

Add one host-memory submission and completion queue, synchronous PCI DMA
ordering, v1 NOP validation, completion publication, queue reset, and CQ
interrupt behavior.  Advertise DMA and polling-safe CQ only with the complete
transport present, and share the generated descriptor definitions.

---
--- a/hw/misc/vams_pcie.c
+++ b/hw/misc/vams_pcie.c
@@ -5,6 +5,7 @@
  */
 
